snippet.title: Genesis Game Boy Trailer Release
snippet.description:
4 action packed levels, collect shields, energy, and power-ups from enemy remains and test your agility to dodge enemy fire, to reach the boss fight at the end of each level.
Are you up to the challenge?
Pre-sale starts on 2021.04.30 on incube8games.com!
